div.p: This diagram illustrates a high-level overview of the application workflow. The application maintains a single renderer instance, a single system instance and a single window instance, each executing its own per-frame loop. To prevent thread contention when these instances interact, thead sychronization mechanism are employed in the they implementation, though these are not depicted in the diagram.
